<h3 id="june-2019---14555">June 2019 - #14555</h3>
<div class="prodSummary">The client required to send notification to HR and employees in case of missing documents.</div>

<p>To implement this, the following are done.</p>
<ol>
  <li>Added a new category named “Missing Personal Record Notification” in Email settings.</li>
  <li>Execute the REPX file for the Custom Report.</li>
  <li>Run three scripts for displaying the custom report created in the email settings and for displaying the new category created in the email settings.</li>
</ol>

